<p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 25px; color: #1c3f94; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Solar power is a miracle. That&rsquo;s how it feels.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">This life-giving ball of fire rises in the east and sets in the west every day of every year, and with the simple technology of solar panels on your roof, it can power your entire home with free electricity. No fuels. No emissions. Just free electricity.</p>
<p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 25px; color: #1c3f94; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">{{lead.First Name:default=Friend}}, we have dedicated ourselves to making this miracle come true for you...</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">...in whatever way makes the most sense for you, your home, and your finances. We want to help you make this happen. In fact, we want to make getting solar power from us one of the most deeply satisfying decisions you&rsquo;ve ever made.</p>
